    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/90763651e014dfe4a1c4d5835d9b00f2.poster.avif?t=1758538212\" width=680 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/90763651e014dfe4a1c4d5835d9b00f2.webm?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/90763651e014dfe4a1c4d5835d9b00f2.mp4?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>WorldShards is a sandbox MMORPG set in a fantasy world that consists of flying islands. This once prosperous planet, populated with furry meowkles, was shattered into pieces in a terrible cat-a-strophe and was then subjected to an invasion by brutal usurpers – the wargs. Players will have to explore fragments of an ancient world, fight back against the wargs and their treacherous king, and find a way to restore the world of meowkles to its former glory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore the world</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/574cb1d7ee27bfc809697fc8f66ce835.poster.avif?t=1758538212\" width=680 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/574cb1d7ee27bfc809697fc8f66ce835.webm?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/574cb1d7ee27bfc809697fc8f66ce835.mp4?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Remnants of the ancient world hold many secrets and mysteries. Use the customizable teleportation system to generate islands best suited to your current goals and play style. Solve various puzzles and complete quests to earn valuable rewards.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gather resources</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/f8a9b3cf9149daac546b81081a196a4e.poster.avif?t=1758538212\" width=680 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/f8a9b3cf9149daac546b81081a196a4e.webm?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/f8a9b3cf9149daac546b81081a196a4e.mp4?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Extract and process resources, unlock new crafting recipes, create unique items, and trade with other players at the auction! The player driven economy will provide a dynamic and self-regulating marketplace where everyone has a chance to advance themselves without &quot;pay to win&quot; mechanics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Develop your base with help from your furry friends</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/9871c658d0ee8e297f6a46c5899c69ac.poster.avif?t=1758538212\" width=680 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/9871c658d0ee8e297f6a46c5899c69ac.webm?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/9871c658d0ee8e297f6a46c5899c69ac.mp4?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>An entire flying island at your disposal where you can build your home, process your resources and set-up crafting stations to make better equipment and weapons. But you are not alone! Find and recruit adorable meowkles as you travel the world. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/5f005ebb21eb9d42af6705dde6d90757.poster.avif?t=1758538212\" width=680 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/5f005ebb21eb9d42af6705dde6d90757.webm?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/5f005ebb21eb9d42af6705dde6d90757.mp4?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>These NPCs will ensure your operations run smoothly back home. Not only are they a great source of entertainment that will delight you with their presence but they also provide you with various enhancements and additional possibilities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight the invaders</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/3aef5f71fb17c97ac33f15fea9e4e64b.poster.avif?t=1758538212\" width=680 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/3aef5f71fb17c97ac33f15fea9e4e64b.webm?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/3aef5f71fb17c97ac33f15fea9e4e64b.mp4?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A levelless character progression system – your skills and play style will depend purely on the weapons and equipment you choose to craft and use. Defeat monsters in dynamic and challenging battles. Use stealth, gadgets and various consumables. Develop unique equipment and create your own tactics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play solo or with friends</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/eda7225126b40f26dba2f2d1d043f3b2.poster.avif?t=1758538212\" width=680 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/eda7225126b40f26dba2f2d1d043f3b2.webm?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156390/extras/eda7225126b40f26dba2f2d1d043f3b2.mp4?t=1758538212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It is entirely possible to accomplish everything in the game solo but the experience becomes even better with friends! Explore islands, gather resources and fight monsters together, form a clan of like-minded players and show your superiority!",
